{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a modern foldable (accordion-style) product description section with smooth open/close animation. Use clean typography and soft blue shadow highlights on hover. Below it, add a product reviews section that displays star ratings only (★★★★★) without text reviews. Stars should glow subtly on hover, use a premium blue gradient, and feel minimal, fast, and mobile-friendly. Design should look professional, e-commerce ready, and conversion-focused.
